Bases: object

Parse TL1 data and return dictionaries of results.

add_model(model, command_file)[source]¶

Add commands for a new equipment type to the TL1Parser Args:

model (str): Equipment type that commands are valid for command_file (str): XML file containing command formats
parse(model, tid, command, line)[source]¶

Parse given response line and return dictionary containing the results Args:

model (str): Equipment type that response is from tid (str): TID that response is from command (str): name of the command (RTRV-VERSION, etc) line (str): response line returned from TL1 execution
Returns:
parsed (dict): contains all the parsed arguments as key/value
parse_raw(model, raw_data)[source]¶

model (str): Equipment type that this response is from raw_data (str): raw, multi-line response from TL1 connection
Returns:
